# Xcode user files
# --------------------------------------------------

*.xcuserstate
*.xcuserdata
*.xcscmblueprint

# Allow shared schemes
!*.xcodeproj/xcshareddata/
!*.xcodeproj/xcshareddata/xcschemes/


